{"tid":2422843,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[已知錯同反省]未交19/20既稅同報稅表...有冇得唔硬食","createTime":"2021-02-25T13:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T09:58:20.000Z","uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"03d154463cd59dfdd7ae452cb6e4c20323eee074","tid":2422843,"uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T13:19:07.000Z","msg":"頭先收到稅局既信，我真心以為終於要報稅<br />\n點知佢係話我19/20既稅未報要罰$600，我登入先睇到原來我真係唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明19年都記得要報稅但上年完全冇左回事<br />\n<br />\n罰$600都冇咩問題，但我睇到張稅單差不多4萬蚊，我就走去計<br />\n發現佢估稅單係唔會扣你既免稅額，就咁計你年收入...暫繳稅都係冇計免稅額個數<br />\n本來我19/20應該唔洗交稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，暫繳稅如果計免稅額應該都只係要交萬3左右（定係暫繳稅本身係唔係都唔會計你免稅額?)<br />\n但依家要我嘔接近4皮出黎....暫繳稅我當我預先比突都冇所謂<br />\n但19/20本身唔洗交稅變左要比成皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已知錯同反省，完全冇諗過報稅收唔到信...出估稅單個時又收唔到信，自己又衰真係冇上網check<br />\n如果反對估稅要係發出估稅單內一個月提出，依家已經過左3個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我打算首先好好地交住依4萬表示我誠意，唔係刻意唔交稅，再寫信認衰仔，退返比我有冇機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166eab2249a8f4bbe50e4e10b071d87960721036","tid":2422843,"uid":89557,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T00:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ac7562c33be9563f7541dce00ef593955847d4","tid":2422843,"uid":125731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:13:34.000Z","msg":"點登入睇？<br />\n佢話要密碼但唔記左又要郵寄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d917f41ad7ececb4f927ed9ad78f841a8f29820","tid":2422843,"uid":35818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:25:20.000Z","msg":"填報稅表+反對通知書最底寫理由點解遲交<br />\n稅款到期交咗先，做完修訂會退票<br />\n態度好啲通常都會幫你做，不過預等好耐先會收到結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319b9193644b0d77c1f5b6711e6a82c54cce45b7","tid":2422843,"uid":125731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:19:53.000Z","msg":"我都遲交左，佢幫我評稅埋，<br />\n我現在登入左入去稅務易，搵唔到邊到填返報稅表<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ecd3d69f5d218c4c8527acda2b5726c00c97c8","tid":2422843,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03d154463cd59dfdd7ae452cb6e4c20323eee074","tid":2422843,"uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T13:19:07.000Z","msg":"頭先收到稅局既信，我真心以為終於要報稅<br />\n點知佢係話我19/20既稅未報要罰$600，我登入先睇到原來我真係唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明19年都記得要報稅但上年完全冇左回事<br />\n<br />\n罰$600都冇咩問題，但我睇到張稅單差不多4萬蚊，我就走去計<br />\n發現佢估稅單係唔會扣你既免稅額，就咁計你年收入...暫繳稅都係冇計免稅額個數<br />\n本來我19/20應該唔洗交稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，暫繳稅如果計免稅額應該都只係要交萬3左右（定係暫繳稅本身係唔係都唔會計你免稅額?)<br />\n但依家要我嘔接近4皮出黎....暫繳稅我當我預先比突都冇所謂<br />\n但19/20本身唔洗交稅變左要比成皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已知錯同反省，完全冇諗過報稅收唔到信...出估稅單個時又收唔到信，自己又衰真係冇上網check<br />\n如果反對估稅要係發出估稅單內一個月提出，依家已經過左3個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我打算首先好好地交住依4萬表示我誠意，唔係刻意唔交稅，再寫信認衰仔，退返比我有冇機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:23:54.000Z","msg":"貼你張單上黎 幫你計計"},{"pid":"7fb442d4c0f7587ed58605269936f3b2bb168924","tid":2422843,"uid":264301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4095b8bad85b6b550b639927e81b3e7bbdb5105","tid":2422843,"uid":264301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fb442d4c0f7587ed58605269936f3b2bb168924","tid":2422843,"uid":264301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17c7706c24c0e734807bd6b3a4fcbfbb6280b93","tid":2422843,"uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:43:24.000Z","msg":"唔該哂咁多位巴絲打<br />\n我琴晚交哂所有稅啦，諗住寄返張野比佢，再等佢評過再退錢<br />\n應該證明到我唔係刻意唔交掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過白痴一問，佢張反對評稅表有得比你選擇「反對評稅」定係「修訂評稅」<br />\n兩者有咩分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c9ffae369f0ac55f39868f5100a87c4af4a7a4","tid":2422843,"uid":39712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T14:42:55.000Z","msg":"巴打我同你一9樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上兩個星期先發現冇交到報稅表到...比佢亂咁估變左要交多好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲過哂反對期限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我已經即刻報番同照交左先...想問下你最後有冇打過比稅局問過係咪有得照反對叫佢重新評稅<br />\n<br />\n早兩日仲收到封信話我遲報稅話要罰1200...雖然係自己錯但真心肉赤<br />\n<br />\n真心唔求免左個罰款只求仲有機會重新評過可以退番交多嗰d比我...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80df8a194132b740abc1705f168ce1c138421df9","tid":2422843,"uid":295532,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T15:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194c33cb3d790855c6bb9bafb0195f3f9f25021d","tid":2422843,"uid":57088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80df8a194132b740abc1705f168ce1c138421df9","tid":2422843,"uid":295532,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T15:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T03:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa13500bea60d14e0fbb958b9d5165826c20dc5","tid":2422843,"uid":