":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3572b45f041dab4c3b05b53e370cc1599ea65863","tid":2422843,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:19:51.000Z","msg":"姐係91年4月到20年4月？"},{"pid":"83c065dd36ef83d6b22a9442abb84fc895fef323","tid":2422843,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fb442d4c0f7587ed58605269936f3b2bb168924","tid":2422843,"uid":264301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"我想問遲交報稅表個六百蚊罰款如果上訴失敗會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係交返六百蚊定要上庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48bb5d4df23253b574d7e700bbdaa0baa368cf5","tid":2422843,"uid":264301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83c065dd36ef83d6b22a9442abb84fc895fef323","tid":2422843,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fb442d4c0f7587ed58605269936f3b2bb168924","tid":2422843,"uid":264301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"我想問遲交報稅表個六百蚊罰款如果上訴失敗會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係交返六百蚊定要上庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal